{"tid":1640682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五大訴求不斷比人帶風向改緊","createTime":"2019-10-09T05:17:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T07:38:34.000Z","uid":149652,"like":13,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"e6796e69d59921e80d233db91c03e43e9123ae32","tid":1640682,"uid":149652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:17:05.000Z","msg":"唔好再比三毛帶風向<br />\n<br />\n佢地專登將好大機會爭取到既訴求，換做極難做到既訴求，令執政者可以順理成章咁無視我地訴求。從而令我地一個訴求都爭取唔到！！！<br />\n<br />\n上一次己經將第五訴求，林奠落台帶風台轉做雙普選，令到林奠可以無壓力咁樣繼續留任賣港。令我地間接變左幫共匪保住個林奠，比個八婆繼續攬住警犬，唔成立獨立調查，繼續推監控街燈，急批明日大愚。<br />\n<br />\n衣家就有人改緊獨立調查做解散警隊，佢地咩居心，求下大家諗一諗。"},{"pid":"1c73c7dea2c4e3dc19ce8d66ce83a5e05e3e8f5f","tid":1640682,"uid":73915,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:18:14.000Z","msg":"唔要林鄭下台係一致共識"},{"pid":"7e484087efaa91f88fc1f076f55ad4a0d129971d","tid":1640682,"uid":149652,"like":0,"dislike":23,"score":-23,"quote":{"pid":"1c73c7dea2c4e3dc19ce8d66ce83a5e05e3e8f5f","tid":1640682,"uid":73915,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:18:14.000Z","msg":"唔要林鄭下台係一致共識"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:19:11.000Z","msg":"係因為己經比人帶左風向"},{"pid":"78e55088ad312580ad288dda53debd0bce54a63c","tid":1640682,"uid":79563,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"7e484087efaa91f88fc1f076f55ad4a0d129971d","tid":1640682,"uid":149652,"like":0,"dislike":23,"score":-23,"quote":{"pid":"1c73c7dea2c4e3dc19ce8d66ce83a5e05e3e8f5f","tid":1640682,"uid":73915,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:18:14.000Z","msg":"唔要林鄭下台係一致共識"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:19:11.000Z","msg":"係因為己經比人帶左風向"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:20:09.000Z","msg":"你條白痴收皮啦<br />\n<br />\n林鄭下台, 何君堯上, 有乜撚用？"},{"pid":"41ee3f3c2a150a76bab08100e88ed5eb6516369a","tid":1640682,"uid":5258,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:20:39.000Z","msg":"你都on9<br />\n林鄭落台後仲有千千萬萬個林鄭<br />\n唔改變個制度根本無撚用"},{"pid":"9a496705fad8d4fc3354e19c5b569f7ecbea8286","tid":1640682,"uid":81273,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:20:45.000Z","msg":"樓主就係帶風向既五毛<br />\n係人都知林鄭係扯線公仔<br />\n係人都知獨立調查唔包生仔冇撚用<br />\n係人都知對中國人要拆屋頂<br />\n你弱智？"},{"pid":"ce3621a90778cdbbb01064eef09ea3532f0e785c","tid":1640682,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:21:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">全球「和尼畫」<br />\n#XinniethePooh Challenge</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rG1sQ5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrG1sQ5b.jpg&h=d6b3d577&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K9NvORS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9NvORS.jpg&h=fcaaa2a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「和尼畫」挑戰<br />\n1.畫出你心中所想的維尼圖<br />\n2.留下你想對習維尼講嘅說話<br />\n3.放上ig、fb、twitter，tag #XinniethePooh<br />\n4.tag 1-3個你想佢一齊畫維尼嘅朋友<br />\n5.被tag嘅朋友一齊畫維尼，讓愛與維尼佔領地球，推到畀習維尼本人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「Xinnie the Pooh」Challenge<br />\n1. Draw your own &quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot;<br />\n2. Write down what do you want to tell Chairman Xi<br />\n3. Post your work on instagram, facebook and twitter with tag #Xinnie the Pooh<br />\n4. Tag up to 3 more friends to ask them draw together!<br />\n5. Those who are tagged also join to draw Xinnie the Pooh, keep drawing until Chairman Xi can see our works!!"},{"pid":"3faed9bb30a177d0f7e786cb1f16e8240f6beefd","tid":1640682,"uid":235015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:21:28.000Z","msg":"由頭到尾到係要雙普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />林鄭落唔落台冇分別"},{"pid":"a5b8214052ed35fd970169dd4850fc3879af9b86","tid":1640682,"uid":5258,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:21:46.000Z","msg":"做五毛做到咁低級就咪學人出post"},{"pid":"e833f20f7c00dcc870f1358c45c8f36f67bfc201","tid":1640682,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:21:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>衣家就有人改緊獨立調查做解散警隊，佢地咩居心，求下大家諗一諗。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n調你老母查咩？<br />\n<br />\n查完一輪, OK, 結論無乜大問題, 下次改善吓啦<br />\n<br />\n有乜意思呀？<br />\n<br />\n唔駛調查啦, 浪費時間, 證據確鑿, 直接行動啦"},{"pid":"42593716610de39111c3e23996e7ec31fd125814","tid":1640682,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:22:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拉"},{"pid":"f52ce5eb0ea2c07362b0a9673f4f707c02c9d8e6","tid":1640682,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:22:42.000Z","msg":"就快世界大戰都仲講緊五大訴求"},{"pid":"a74193bd9397b3656ecc0a6d5852c7e560c6e315","tid":1640682,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:22:43.000Z","msg":"戇鳩 無普選佢下台有乜意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e9b71dece79e3f92b7a5afccf308defd78c98ba","tid":1640682,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3faed9bb30a177d0f7e786cb1f16e8240f6beefd","tid":1640682,"uid":235015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:21:28.000Z","msg":"由頭到尾到係要雙普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />林鄭落唔落台冇分別"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:22:52.000Z","msg":"係毒果日報一開波, 寫「林鄭落台」<br />\n<br />\n第二日已經被人屌到上天花板<br />\n<br />\n10月都仲有人講, 唔知係五毛定係白痴仔"},{"pid":"64b8ad931530905c668a2818a0d71714f3f7cb19","tid":1640682,"uid":258696,"like":1,